title: Qualy #43 - What are Peter's thoughts on fasting and ketosis for females?
content: This episode discusses Peter's thoughts on fasting and ketosis for females. He explains that women may need to be more cautious with fasting and ketosis due to hormonal differences. He recommends that women who want to try fasting or ketosis should work with a healthcare provider to monitor their progress and make adjustments as needed. Additionally, he suggests that women who are pregnant or breastfeeding should avoid fasting and ketosis altogether.

title: What is Qualys?
content: Qualys is a subscriber-exclusive podcast, released Tuesday through Friday, and published exclusively on our private, subscriber-only podcast feed. Qualys is short-hand for “qualifying round,” which are typically the fastest laps driven in a race car—done before the race to determine starting position on the grid for race day. The Qualys are short (i.e., “fast”), typically less than ten minutes, and highlight the best questions, topics, and tactics discussed on The Drive.
